trailingComments.value:
*
 * Do nothing if x is empty or n is zero.
 * Rotate left n steps if n is positive.
 * Rotate right n steps if n is negative.
 *
 * @param {Node} x The current first node.
 * @param {number} n
 * @return {Node} The new first node.
